{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"alias":"only-crave-art","description":"## Context\nThe plan-review gate (`5fd2`) reviews ONE ticket's plan in isolation. It deliberately does NOT detect SEMANTIC\noverlap, duplication, or undeclared dependencies BETWEEN SEPARATE tickets across the store. Existing coverage is\npartial and different in kind: `G4` checks consistency WITHIN one epic's children; `next_batch` schedules around\nDETERMINISTIC file-impact conflicts; `duplicates`/`supersedes` are MANUAL links. The residual — semantic overlap /\nduplication / hidden cross-ticket dependency across UNRELATED tickets — is uncovered.\n\n## Scope\nThis is explicitly OUTSIDE the plan-review gate (a per-ticket reviewer cannot see the whole store). It is\nstore-wide and applies BOTH cross-epic AND between non-epic tickets that may overlap (not just \"cross-epic\" —\nany two tickets, epic or not). Closer to a store-health / scheduling capability (`validate` / `next_batch`)\nthan to a plan-review criterion. (Was the former plan-review follow-on \"F7\"; spun out per review.)\n\n## Success Criteria\n- Surface semantically-overlapping or duplicate tickets, and undeclared cross-ticket dependencies, across the\n  whole store (any pair — cross-epic or non-epic), for human confirmation.\n- Low false-flagging of legitimately-related-but-distinct work; suggests `duplicates`/`supersedes`/`depends_on`\n  links rather than auto-applying them.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Detects semantic overlap/duplication between separate tickets store-wide (cross-epic AND non-epic), beyond deterministic file-impact and manual links.\n- [ ] Surfaces candidate duplicate/supersede/dependency relations for human confirmation (does not auto-mutate links).\n- [ ] Explicitly a store-health capability, NOT a per-ticket plan-review criterion; does not run inside the `5fd2` gate.","id":"bd83-c56f-1f72-4ef2","parent_id":"","priority":3,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"epic","title":"Cross-ticket overlap & dependency detection (store-wide: cross-epic + non-epic) — outside the plan-review gate"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782064359280454001,"uuid":"f8018c7d-af7f-4d8a-a0b3-1ae17837f26f"}